Class X3dMetadataValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.interactivemesh.jfx.importer.x3d.X3dMetadata

  • public final class X3dMetadataValue
extends X3dMetadata
    Represents a named user data array object. Supported value types are double[], float[], int[], and String[].
    See Also:
